O! Zaboravio sam biskvite.

00:17:20.338 --> 00:17:22.329
Ow!

00:17:26.044 --> 00:17:27.978
Lijepo, ha?

00:17:28.046 --> 00:17:30.276
O, stvarno je dobro.

00:17:31.749 --> 00:17:34.411
Gdje si sakrio korpu, Rede?

00:17:37.655 --> 00:17:41.091
- Evo ti vlažna maramica.

